From c404867135c61b619dad26906fa573a56c63e9ea Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Priyadarshnee Srinivasan <priys@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Fri, 11 Jul 2025 06:27:00 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] UPSTREAM:PROTOCOL:hostapd: Enhance TPE EIRP calculation for
 punctured channels

Previously, the EIRP power in the TPE IE did not account for
the impact of punctured channels. Enhance the logic to determine
the effective non-punctured bandwidth and compute the corresponding EIRP power,
ensuring accurate power representation across all channel configurations.
Define get_lower_bandwidth_puncture_pattern()
to derive the puncture pattern according to the target bandwidth.
Implement hostapd_get_eirp_arr_for_bw() to generate the EIRP array
for TPE IE for both punctured and non-punctured bandwidths.

Fixes: None
